&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;NOTE :&lt;/strong&gt; The widest breakpoint is always named &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;large&lt;/code&gt; and the narrowest &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;small&lt;/code&gt;. You can add any other breakpoint between.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;!-- ## Features

- **No** need to wrap each row nor to add a ```.last``` class on the last column
- **Customizable** : gutter width, columns number, ...
- Add as many breakpoints as you need
- Choose your own class names
- Be **mobile first** or not
- If necessary choose a positionning scheme between inline-block, float and soon **flexbox**
- also : offset classes, visibilty classes, development mode ... --&gt;

