&lt;h2 id=&quot;if-plugged-with-the-media-queries-mixinmqhtml&quot;&gt;If plugged with the &lt;a href=&quot;mq.html&quot;&gt;Media Queries mixin&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Copy the following map in you project :&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-scss&quot; data-lang=&quot;scss&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;$css117-breakpoints&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;medium&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;     &lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;800px&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;small&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;      &lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;500px&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;);&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&quot;else&quot;&gt;else&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You need to create of SASS map of breakpoints called &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;$breakpoints&lt;/code&gt; (name is mandatory).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-scss&quot; data-lang=&quot;scss&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;$breakpoints&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;medium&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;     &lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;800px&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;small&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;      &lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;500px&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;);&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&quot;floats-or-inline-block&quot;&gt;floats or inline-block&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Don’t know the difference between both ? check &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.vanseodesign.com/blog/demo/inline-block/&quot;&gt;this page&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;With &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;inline-block&lt;/code&gt; :
    &lt;ul&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;It allows you to vertically align elements&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Each &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;.col&lt;/code&gt; goes to a new line no matter the heights of previous columns&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Because of the whitespace, &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;font-size&lt;/code&gt; is set to &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;0&lt;/code&gt; in the parent element&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;/ul&gt;
  &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;With &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;floats&lt;/code&gt; :
    &lt;ul&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Each row of columns needs to be wrap within a &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;row&lt;/code&gt; element :&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;/ul&gt;
  &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-html&quot; data-lang=&quot;html&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;row&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;col large-4 medium-6 small-12&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;...&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;col large-4 medium-6 small-12&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;...&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;col large-4 medium-12&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;...&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;row&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;col large-6&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;...&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;col large-6&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;...&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;row&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;col large-5&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;...&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;col large-4&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;...&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;col large-3&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;...&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Soon a &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/css-flexbox-1/&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;flexbox&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt; option will be available.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&quot;if-small-is-true&quot;&gt;If &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;small&lt;/code&gt; is &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;true&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;By default, each column of the &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;small&lt;/code&gt; breakpoints have different sizes, but in actual use, you probably want to set a single width for each column of the small breakpoint.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Therefore you do not need to add the &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;small&lt;/code&gt; classes in your markup :&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-html&quot; data-lang=&quot;html&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;row&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;col large-4 medium-6&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;...&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;col large-4 medium-6&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;...&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;col large-4 medium-12&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;...&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    ...
&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

</description>
