      <item>
        <title>Get started</title>
        <description>&lt;h2 id=&quot;installation&quot;&gt;Installation&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Via bower :&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-cli&quot; data-lang=&quot;cli&quot;&gt;bower install css117&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;or by downloading &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/aastudio/CSS117/archive/master.zip&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;the latest archive&lt;/a&gt; from the Github repo.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&quot;how-to-use&quot;&gt;How to use&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Components are located in the folder : &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;src/partials/&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;@import&lt;/code&gt; the component in your main SASS file (usually &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;main.scss&lt;/code&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Copy its variables (or just the one you need) in your project and remove the &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;!default&lt;/code&gt; flag&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For every components, each variables are gathered in a SASS map :&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-scss&quot; data-lang=&quot;scss&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;$css117-grid&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;nb-of-columns&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;12&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;width&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;1000px&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;gutter-width&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;20px&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;...&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;default&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&quot;example&quot;&gt;Example&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;To install the &lt;a href=&quot;grid.html&quot;&gt;grid&lt;/a&gt; :&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Copy and import in your project : &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;src/partials/components/grid.scss&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-scss&quot; data-lang=&quot;scss&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;@import&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&#39;partials/components/grid&#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Copy its variables in your project and remove the &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;!default&lt;/code&gt; flag&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-scss&quot; data-lang=&quot;scss&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;$css117-grid&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;nb-of-columns&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;	 &lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;12&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;width&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;           &lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;1000px&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;gutter-width&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;	 &lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;20px&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;rowPadding&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; 	 &lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;10px&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;colPadding&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;      &lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;50px&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;rowMarginBottom&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;30px&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;colMarginBottom&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;30px&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;positionScheme&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&#39;inline-block&#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;row&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;             &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&#39;cols&#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;col&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;             &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&#39;col&#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;offsetClass&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;	 &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&#39;offset&#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;centered&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;        &lt;span class=&quot;bp&quot;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;small&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;           &lt;span class=&quot;bp&quot;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;offset&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;          &lt;span class=&quot;bp&quot;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;visibility&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;      &lt;span class=&quot;bp&quot;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;dev&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;             &lt;span class=&quot;bp&quot;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;debug&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;           &lt;span class=&quot;bp&quot;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;);&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;That’s all. Next step, see how to &lt;a href=&quot;grid.html&quot;&gt;set up your html&lt;/a&gt; to use the grid.&lt;/p&gt;

